{"tid":2198169,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"幫同好報名日本書法賽卻搞丟作品 男子自己寫還得獎","createTime":"2020-09-11T07:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T07:50:11.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bbc4bfc5d1fd0ea03f1896d5424c400dc705e3e2","tid":2198169,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:09:34.000Z","msg":"〔記者王定傳／新北報導〕<br />\n<br />\n---------<br />\n---------------<br />\n---------<br />\n<br />\n檢警調查，去年7月，周女因為想參加「日本第71回全日學生書道展」，得知有熱心的同好要幫忙報名，因此把作品寄給周男，委託他寄至日本參賽。<br />\n<br />\n怎料，周男卻不慎遺失周女的書法作品，事後竟異想天開，自己拿毛筆書寫，再冒用周女名義落款，把作品寄到日本參賽，後來還真的得獎。<br />\n<br />\n周女為此親赴日本領獎，驚覺展出的作品，根本不是她的筆跡，因此提告，周男坦承犯行，法官審理後依偽造私文書罪，判他2個月徒刑，可上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/3287919\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F3287919&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fpS9c5E4FlifGpQIAZCXP1E%3D&h=b14fb100\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F3287919&h=035de52b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/3287919</a>"},{"pid":"627bbb59eb8f2c05236aea587ef9893cb24b1aef","tid":2198169,"uid":26752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:47:52.000Z","msg":"賤女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4d5b0c761cdf3c495db027b773f056ceae78e8","tid":2198169,"uid":13936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:50:11.000Z","msg":"幫佢贏咪想點<br />\n問都無問就告"}]}